NOLLWOOD actress Adesua Etomi-Wellington has been recognised as a global talent as she makes her debut appearance on the cover of Vogue Magazine. – Husband Banky W took to his social media to gush about his wife’s accomplishment. And fans while cheering the actress on, frowned at the difference in skin tone portrayed by the magazine. Say all you want to say about Nigeria, but you can never take away the fact that the country is richly blessed with a notable number of talents across board. From science and technology, architecture, agriculture and entertainment, there is always a Nigerian that is changing the narrative and striving hard to make a difference. The celebrated Nigerian actress is being recognised along 14 other talented actresses in the world who are being celebrated for their resilience and astounding performances in their acting careers, by world renowned high fashion publishing house, Vogue Magazine.